{"id": 1458, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些打着“健康”旗号吸引你的路数，你会多留个心眼？", "description": "你是怎么着就莫名其妙地为那些或真或假的“健康”买单的？（题图来自：Diego Marmolejo）", "record_count": 15608, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170119083248BjgK8ChTZldEsUIW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-19T17:00:58Z", "questions": [{"id": 1752, "title": "哪些打着“健康”旗号吸引你的路数，你会多留个心眼？", "content": "你见过哪些打着“健康”旗号吸引你的套路？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 155587, "content": "偷换概念型，宣称“不含任何化学物质”", "image": "img/option/option/20170119080606FsdzH0IkQbcR29PV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155588, "content": "和天然食品套近乎，洗洁精从大米里面萃取之类的", "image": "img/option/option/20170119080736sO0n8Eju15KoLbAg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155589, "content": "和植物套近乎，护肤品包装上有各种没听过的花花草草", "image": "img/option/option/20170119081701Qaifr7JNyHtBoZY0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155591, "content": "术语高深类，塑料不含BPA，果汁是NFC的", "image": "img/option/option/20170119082421GHLW4XcJVAiCEmuz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155592, "content": "给生活做加法，告诉你需要补充维生素ABCDE", "image": "img/option/option/201701190828075PEHlSxW3vLZjVbG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155593, "content": "恐吓型，如果你再不用我们的健康产品，就……", "image": "img/option/option/20170119082923d2XshaUDncwoJi1l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155594, "content": "“那你到底在吃什么”类，低酒精酒，低钠盐", "image": "img/option/option/20170119083053Kyd6t0ifQxlUkLRH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155595, "content": "返璞归真型，原产地直送，手工、真材实料", "image": "img/option/option/20170119083151wJkZmTbug3LFQ4or.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}